Mosquitor flies out of the predacon base. "Die invaders!!" He screams as he 
shoots acid at the People's Group, mindlessly trying to hit all of them.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Shredder growls as he hears the shots from a hallway in the predacon base. He 
takes off at a run to the nearest exit, arming his rifle.
